Flycatcher: 
<figureCitation id="6FED0192FFF7B54BAC3DFC0BFE511E55" box="[295,435,2067,2091]" captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="12.[168,230,1869,1889]" captionTargetBox="[169,1418,160,1843]" captionTargetId="figure-10@12.[168,1419,160,1843]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="Figure 4. Photos of birds mistnetted during our survey of Vanuatu: A. Melanesian Flycatcher Myiagra caledonica (male). B. Melanesian Flycatcher Myiagra caledonica (female). C. Pacific Robin Petroica multicolor feminina. D. Pacific Robin Petroica multicolor ambrynensis. E. Yellow-fronted White-eye Zosterops flavifrons. F. Island Thrush Turdus poliocephalus efatensis. G Royal Parrotfinch Erythrura regia." pageId="11" pageNumber="766">Figure 4A, B</figureCitation>
